== Local installation

=== OSX, Linux

Something like:
[source,shell]
--------------------
$ git clone git://github.com/tricycle/predictionbook.git
$ cd predictionbook
$ bin/setup
$ Run `EDITOR='any of your choise (nano, vim)' bundle exec rails credentials:edit`
$ Copy content from credentials.yml.sample
$ Paste contents in the encrypted file and save
$ rails spec # run specs
$ script/rails server
$ ^Z # ctrl+z
$ bg
$ open http://127.0.0.1:3000/
$ fg
--------------------

=== Google Analytics

* In file "config/credentials.yml.enc"
  + replace [your_analytics_tracker_id] with your Google Analytics tracker id
